":1873194,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"確診果個好似唔係住果度<br />\nd人話係家居隔離wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2979af40a2a51839c3926bf2b01bc0605b1a3f","tid":1873194,"uid":309465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:31:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ab26ad1dcbbe8cb3fb7f880a3c69987f7d14e91","tid":1873194,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc08aef05d56369fffd488bd166ad3dfdf511182","tid":1873194,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"確診果個好似唔係住果度<br />\nd人話係家居隔離wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"區議員講到咁firm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93141759de37328728a2efcd0d2fbeb263dd12b9","tid":1873194,"uid":87723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:03:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7243337dc78a9fb19898bde2f4a3b695e056c068","tid":1873194,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T16:27:42.000Z","msg":"知道大家好多疑問一次過回答大家<br />\n<br />\n1）消息來源問題：<br />\n消息是由患者家人聯絡我們提供，並告知於今日傍晚時份確診。<br />\n<br />\n2）為何政府未有公佈我們就公告？<br />\n現時政府仍未將此患者列入確診名單，我們亦無法知悉政府更新名單的時間係點，相信政府今晚或者聽日，就會將佢列入為確診名單。<br />\n因為家屬和我們都希望街坊能及早知道，及早清潔及加強防疫措施，所以家屬一知道確診就和我們聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n3） 相關的消毒清潔工作：<br />\n今日法團已經在東平樓大堂及相關樓層進行一次徹底消毒，及早清潔，減低傳染風險。法團亦都會再加強東平樓的消毒工作，以防萬一。<br />\n<br />\n4）其家人隔離問題：<br />\n抱歉因私隱關係，我們不能公開事主單位。暫時得知與患者有密切接觸的家人已要求進行20日家居隔離。若然親屬有任何物資上要求，我哋會盡力提供。<br />\n<br />\n5）知道大家好擔心，所以大家更加要做好自己和家人的消毒清潔，減少外出，並帶備口罩，多洗手，減低風險。"},{"pid":"128e96e46b42e033b8bc1b010a9c91e5988febbf","tid":1873194,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab26ad1dcbbe8cb3fb7f880a3c69987f7d14e91","tid":1873194,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc08aef05d56369fffd488bd166ad3dfdf511182","tid":1873194,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"確診果個好似唔係住果度<br />\nd人話係家居隔離wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"區議員講到咁firm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"但我再睇係同住家人要隔20日<br />\n即係個患者都住果度<br />\n有朋友住同一層打過去管理處問<br />\n管理處答佢唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1260b830e7da5dec67fe4d001b13fb44d088c7f","tid":1873194,"uid":130641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"128e96e46b42e033b8bc1b010a9c91e5988febbf","tid":1873194,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab26ad1dcbbe8cb3fb7f880a3c69987f7d14e91","tid":1873194,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc08aef05d56369fffd488bd166ad3dfdf511182","tid":1873194,"uid":10241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"確診果個好似唔係住果度<br />\nd人話係家居隔離wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"區議員講到咁firm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:22:54.000Z","msg":"但我再睇係同住家人要隔20日<br />\n即係個患者都住果度<br />\n有朋友住同一層打過去管理處問<br />\n管理處答佢唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等聽日公布"}]}